body:
My altered version of lyrics for ‘The Man’ by The Killers, but even better.

Also, listen to the song and read the lyrics along with it. It makes it soooo much better.

Anyways, behold. ‘Kylo Rennn, aand Rey’ by me.

So, remember to listen to the song as you read. Okay enjoy

Kylo Renn, aand Rey…

Another scared boy, with blood on his hands

Them leather boots, A cape and commands

The Siths in the ring, He carries the crown

Nothing can break, nothing can break Ren down

Don’t need no advice, Rens got a plan

(Kill Luke)

Another direction, the lay of the land

(Kill Luke)

He knows the scores, like the palm of Rey’s hands

Them other boys, He don’t give a damn

Kylo Rennn, aand Rey, n-n-nothing can break, nothing can break them down

Kylo Rennn, and Rey, &

N-Nothing can break, you, can’t, break, them, downnnn

He got gas in the tank

He got an army and a base

He’s got news for you baby, you’re looking at her man

He’s got star killer base

He’s got a galactic name

He’s got news for you baby, you’re looking at her man

When it comes to Friday, He always works

don’t try to teach him, He’s got nothing to learn

‘Cause baby he’s gifted

Rey knows what I mean ;)

He’s got Star Killer base

He don’t feel no pain

Who’s the man with the plan?

He’s the man

He’s the man

He’s the man

Hes the man

He’s got a scarred up face

Hes got news for you baby, you’re looking at her man

He’s Headed to the hall of…FAME

Hes got news for you baby, you’re looking at her man

Right hand to God

Sith Lord commands

Snokes testimony, but he will withstand

He’s the man, He’s the man

He’s the man

Tomorrow I’ll work on getting all the doors and vents and pipes painted up silver and hit them with a wash or two.

summary: How to celebrate Star Wars -day? Buy stuff!! I was going to buy just the Imperial Raider class corvette (the pack included the...
body:
How to celebrate Star Wars -day? Buy stuff!! I was going to buy just the Imperial Raider class corvette (the pack included the TIE advanced) but the new trilogy hero ship -pack (Millenial Falcon and Poe’s X-wing) and Kylo’s TIE Silencer somehow eneded up into the order as well…

(How could I live without owning that beautiful raider class ship when the Inferno Squad had one as their home -ship???That’s more than enough of a reason for the money spending!!)

summary: Una nueva trilogía de Star Wars iniciará en 2022
title: Una nueva trilogía de Star Wars iniciará en 2022
body:
Una nueva trilogía de #StarWars iniciará en 2022

Anunciado por Disney, cada nueva película se estrenará en el fin de semana previo a la Navidad cada dos años a partir de 2022; lo que significa que una nueva película de Star Wars saldrá en 2022, 2024 y 2026. Estas películas aún no han sido tituladas, pero definitivamente habrá algo más alla de esta última trilogía que acaba este año.
